name: Rosario Dawson
description:
A commission of @Zorglub.

Rosario Dawson is an American actress of Cuban and Puerto Rican descent, known for her roles in many films, such as Sin City or Men in Black, and TV shows such as The Mandalorian.

This TI has been a tough one to train... I've had to repeat the process from scratch a couple of times, mainly because I couldn't get the eyes right. Reduced the dataset to 12 images, then removed some more pics and added a few new ones... I'm satisfied with the final results, but I may still update the embedding at a later point.

This is step 1325 of a TI trained on a dataset of 15 images. I used my standard settings.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

How to create a good prompt using my TIs

You're obviously free to experiment, but bear in mind that my TIs are trained with a more or less fixed phrasing, that normally starts with:

"photo of EMBEDDING_NAME, a woman"

So I recommend always starting your prompt like that and then building the rest of the prompt from there. For instance, "photo of (r0sd4wn-1325:0.99), a woman, RAW, close portrait photo, long brown coat, ((turtleneck sweater:1.2), trousers, long haircut, slim body, (high detailed skin:1.2), 8k uhd, dslr, soft lighting, high quality, film grain, Fujifilm XT3 sharp focus, f 5.6"
